g a simple puzzle level with 4-directional movement, and the next second you are in the Platformer with big constructions and moving platforms, or even in a remake of a popular mobile title.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2082580/extras/21ba37e4fc1203fa7c9bac7c760a01f0.avif?t=1772134591\" width=615 height=300 /></span>",
